cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM

The paper deals with image and depth reconstruction, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) categories. The use of convolutional neural networks as a prior for depth reconstruction also involves machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions multi-view stereo, which is related to robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the evaluation of the proposed method involves comparing the quality of 3D models, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
